Package: grendelshiny
Type: Package
Title: Shared Styling for Grendel Shiny Apps
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Rolf", family = "Lindgren", email = "rolf@grendel.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared CSS, JavaScript, and brand assets that give a family of
    Grendel Shiny apps a consistent turquoise-dark visual theme. Provides a
    base design system (layout, typography, form controls, sliders, tabs), a
    small JavaScript utility for managing selectize dropdown state, and the
    canonical Grendel logo mark as a self-contained helper.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: htmltools, base64enc
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
